      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts completed with no critical findings.",
      "rationale": "An independent analyst reviewed all model inputs, contact definitions, boundary condition application, and post-processing macros. Two minor findings (unit label inconsistency in output report, redundant constraint) were corrected prior to final runs. No critical use errors identified."
