    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-fda-osel",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required credibility levels. The Test conditions factor achieves level 2 against a required level of 3; however, the assessment team judges this shortfall to be acceptable because testing was performed at two independent laboratories under the same protocol, providing sufficient inter-laboratory reproducibility evidence, and the single-condition limitation is bounded by the narrow clinical loading envelope of ASTM F1717. Overall credibility is assessed as Medium, consistent with model risk level 3 and medium decision consequence. The submission is accepted for regulatory use.",
